- With remote control you can manage a running pDNSf instance remotely from the Android App
- usefull especially when running the non-Android version without UI
- On the remote version, you want to manage, enable this feature by setting 
  ==> server_remote_ctrl_port = 3333 
- On the client version you want to use for remote controlling set the IP Address to connect to:
  ==> client_remote_ctrl_host = <the IP Address or host on which the remote runs>
- Restart remote and client instance
- From the Android UI use the "remote control" icon to connect


  
